==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Crdit mobilier
<hw>Cr⟦eacute⟧`dit" mo`bi`lier"</hw> <pr>(m?`b?`ly?")</pr>. <ety>[F.
<ets>cr⟦eacute⟧dit</ets> credit & <ets>mobilier</ets> personal,
pertaining to personal property.]</ety> <def>A joint stock company,
formed for general banking business, or for the construction of public
works, by means of loans on personal estate, after the manner of the
<cref>cr⟦eacute⟧dit foncier</cref> on real estate. In practice, however,
this distinction has not been strictly observed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Creditor</ent>⟦br⟧
